        <span>100kr</span>
      </div>

      <div class="price-row">
        <span>Student</span>
        <span>150kr</span>
      </div>

      <div class="price-row">
        <span>Pensionär</span>
        <span>150kr</span>
      </div>

      <p class="price-note">
        *Andra priser gäller under evenemang. Kontakta receptionen för mer info
      </p>
    </section>

  </section>
  </section>

  <section class="kino_box">
    <h2>På kino:</h2>
    <div class="ul_container">
      <ul>
        <li> Resturang</li>
        <li> Bar</li>
        <li> Events</li>
      </ul>
      <ul>
        <li> Barnvagnsbio</li>
